attachments.title: What The Hell Is This Strange Green Glow Inside The Fukushima Plant?
attachments.text: A second robotic probe has investigated the interior of Japan’s stricken Fukushima nuclear power plant. Using its onboard camera, it sent back eerie images of the plant’s interior, including what appears to be a mysterious green glow.
